<%- include('partials/head') %>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<main class="container" style="max-width:780px;padding:40px 20px 60px">
  <h1 style="font-size:26px">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p style="color:var(--text-500);font-size:13px">Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
  <div style="color:var(--text-700);font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.85">
    <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly, including your name, email, phone number, shipping addresses, and payment-related details (such as transaction IDs for manual payment verification — we do not store full card numbers). Vendors additionally provide business information, warehouse details, and payout account information.</p>
    <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>We use your information to process orders, facilitate communication between customers and vendors, calculate and distribute commissions, verify vendor applications, prevent fraud, and improve our platform.</p>
    <h3>3. Information Sharing</h3>
    <p>Order and shipping details are shared with the relevant vendor(s) fulfilling your order. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
    <h3>4. Data Security</h3>
    <p>We use industry-standard practices including encrypted password storage, rate limiting, and role-based access controls to protect your data.</p>
    <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by contacting our support team.</p>
    <h3>6. Cookies</h3>
    <p>We use cookies to maintain your login session and protect against cross-site request forgery. We do not use third-party advertising cookies.</p>
    <h3>7. Contact</h3>
    <p>For privacy-related questions, please reach out via our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
